videos.headline: Middle Tennesse strikes first with Mathers' 20-yard TD
videos.description: I'Tavius Mathers takes the handoff and sweeps right, finding lots of room ahead of him before diving for the goalline to put Middle Tennessee up 7-0.

videos.headline: I'Tavius Mathers runs 20 yds for a TD
videos.description: I'Tavius Mathers run for 20 yds for a TD (Canon Rooker KICK)

videos.headline: Flea-flicker turns into touchdown for Middle Tennessee
videos.description: Middle Tennessee goes to the bag of tricks early by running the flea-flicker to perfection with Brent Stockstill finding Richie James for the 79-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ikem Okeke gets the sack and forces the fumble. Jahlani Tavai recovers the ball.
videos.description: Brent Stockstill sacked by Ikem Okeke for a loss of 5 yards to the MTnSt 30 Brent Stockstill fumbled, forced by Ikem Okeke, recovered by Hawa Jahlani Tavai , return for 0 yards

videos.headline: Dru Brown passes to Metuisela 'Unga for a 18-yard TD
videos.description: Dru Brown pass complete to Metuisela 'Unga for 18 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Jalen Rogers intercepts the ball from Brent Stockstill
videos.description: Brent Stockstill pass intercepted Jalen Rogers return for no gain to the MTnSt 45

videos.headline: Lakalaka punches it in for Hawai'i TD
videos.description: Steven Lakalaka gets the handoff and runs in for the 1-yard touchdown to tie Hawai'i's game with Middle Tennessee at 14.

videos.headline: Metuisela 'Unga with a 24-yard reception for the 1st down
videos.description: Dru Brown pass complete to Metuisela 'Unga for 24 yds to the MTnSt 18 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Brown scores on the keeper for another Hawai'i rush TD
videos.description: Hawai'i makes it 21 straight points when Dru Brown scores on the quarterback keeper to give the Rainbow Warriors their first lead of the game.

videos.headline: Henderson high-steps his way in with a pick-six
videos.description: Hawai'i's makes it 28 straight points when its defense gets in to the act thanks to Trayvon Henderson makes the interception and going 68 the other way to the house, with a high-step celebration thrown in for good measure.

videos.headline: Brent Stockstill completes a pass to Ty Lee for a TD
videos.description: Brent Stockstill pass complete to Ty Lee for 3 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Hawai'i strikes again with long TD before halftime
videos.description: With just 33 seconds left in the half, Dru Brown goes deep to Marcus Kemp, who makes the leaping catch for the 39-yard touchdown to boost Hawai'i's lead to 35-21.

videos.headline: Brent Stockstill 31-yard pass to Richie James for the 1st down
videos.description: Brent Stockstill pass complete to Richie James for 31 yds to the Hawa 44 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Andrews holds on for 10-yard touchdown catch
videos.description: Middle Tennessee cuts into Hawai'i's lead when Brent Stockstill finds Dennis Andrews, who gets crushed in the end zone but holds on for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Hawai'i pulls off tricky fake punt for first down
videos.description: Hawai'I goes into the bag of tricks, lining up Makoa Camanse-Stevens behind the punter and having him take the snap to throw to Ammon Barker for the first down.

videos.headline: Unga hauls in second TD catch for Hawai'i
videos.description: Dru Brown hooks up with Metuisela 'Unga for the second time in the game to boost Hawai'i's lead up to 17 points near the end of the third quarter.

videos.headline: Richie James runs 13 yds for the touchdown
videos.description: Richie James run for 13 yds for a TD (Canon Rooker KICK)

videos.headline: Paul Harris runs 21 yards for the 1st down
videos.description: Paul Harris run for 21 yds to the MTnSt 9 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Collie stretches out to score 4-yard TD for Hawai'i
videos.description: Dru Brown racks up his fourth touchdown pass of the game, finding Dylan Collie who stretches out to the goal line to score for Hawai'i.
